# Core Standards

- Stack: Astro (SSR/SSG), TypeScript strict, Tailwind CSS, Supabase.
- Prefer explicit types. Avoid `any` unless the reason is documented.
- Use `??` and `?.` instead of manual null guards when it keeps the code clearer.
- Keep all files UTF-8 encoded. When writing files via Node, use `'utf8'`.
- If mojibake appears, run `node scripts/fix-mojibake.cjs`.
- Run `npx astro check` after larger changes when practical.
